Michael Saylor.</p> <p>The Sock Puppet said to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/661042546/image_661042546.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742952-did-we-learn-anything-from-sock-puppet-2000", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 17:30:00"}, {"id": "4743032", "title": "Used Vehicle Prices Turn Into Inflation Headwind, After Historic 2-Year Plunge Helped Power The 'Deceleration' Of Core CPI", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Happy saleswoman working at a car dealership\" data-id=\"1473399378\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"954px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Hispanolistic/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Prices are rising again, amid tight supply, sharply reduced flow through the used vehicle pipeline, and strong demand.</em></p> <p>Prices of used vehicle sold at auctions across the US jumped by 1.3% in November from October, seasonally adjusted, continuing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473399378/image_1473399378.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743032-used-vehicle-prices-turn-into-inflation-headwind-historic-2-year-plunge-deceleration-core-cpi", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 17:25:00"}, {"id": "4743016", "title": "Starbucks' Gamble: Low Hedge Ratio Amid Surging Green Coffee Prices (Strong Sell)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Red arrow chart graph soar rising up on coffee roasted arabica bean background.\" data-id=\"1617624935\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Pla2na/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Investment Summary</strong></h2> <p>This is a follow-up to our latest \"<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741759-starbucks-predicament-chinese-rivals-poised-to-shake-up-us-market-strong-sell\">Strong Sell</a>\" recommendation on Starbucks (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SBUX\" title=\"Starbucks Corporation\">SBUX</a></span>) as I believe the recent spike in coffee bean prices will further pressure Starbucks margin in the next</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1617624935/image_1617624935.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743016-starbucks-gamble-low-hedge-ratio-amid-surging-green-coffee-prices-strong-sell", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 17:16:51"}, {"id": "4742932", "title": "Main Street Vs. Fidus Investment: Both Are Top Class, One Is At Better Price", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A couple under a red umbrella. Health and life insurance concept.\" data-id=\"1956825007\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1027px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1956825007/image_1956825007.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uplo