age\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334957523/image_1334957523.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334957523/image_1334957523.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334957523/image_1334957523.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334957523/image_1334957523.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334957523/image_1334957523.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334957523/image_1334957523.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334957523/image_1334957523.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334957523/image_1334957523.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">niwate bunlue</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Written by Sam Kovacs</em></p> <h2>Introduction: Time in the market or timing the market?</h2> <p>We all know the old investment adage: time in the market beats timing the market.</p> <p>The idea is that you're better off being exposed to equities 100% of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334957523/image_1334957523.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743014-dont-miss-the-dividend-train-2-top-buys-to-end-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 17:04:40"}, {"id": "4743011", "title": "Bitcoin Could Significantly Outperform The Stock Market In 2025", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https: