tic.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156834628/image_2156834628.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743011-bitcoin-significantly-outperform-stock-market-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 17:00:25"}, {"id": "4743008", "title": "MAGS: Back To Its Best", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rolling the dice\" data-id=\"1422219755\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1014px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Roundhill Magnificent Seven ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MAGS\" title=\"Roundhill Magnificent Seven ETF\">MAGS</a></span>) had a slow start to H2, but is now back to its former ways, leading the market and outperforming. This article looks at the reasons behind the rally and why it could continue.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1422219755/image_1422219755.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743008-mags-back-to-its-best", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:52:35"}, {"id": "4743007", "title": "ClearPoint: Fundamentals Continue To Improve", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Digital Brain With Connections\" data-id=\"2107031844\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">imaginima</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>While ClearPoint's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CLPT\" title=\"ClearPoint Neuro, Inc.\">CLPT</a></span>) share price has stagnated in recent months, even as the broader market has surged higher, there have been a number of positive developments. In particular, ClearPoint's laser therapy and drug delivery businesses appear set to continue driving strong</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2107031844/image_2107031844.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743007-clearpoint-fundamentals-continue-to-improve", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:50:34"}, {"id": "4743020", "title": "VersaBank 2024 Q4 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by VersaBank in conjunction with their 2024 Q4 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106079\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743020-versabank-2024-q4-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:36:14"}, {"id": "4742943", "title": "Retail Sector Earnings Roundup: Analyzing The Holiday Season Winners And Losers", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Shop owner handing bag to smiling client after shopping in clothing boutique\" data-id=\"1217476252\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The holiday shopping season is in full swing, and a broad range of retailers have reported results, with many surpassing sales and earnings expectations. The macroeconomic environment continues to favor retailers with a strong value-driven product mix, benefiting giants like Walmart (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1217476252/image_1217476252.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742943-retail-sector-earnings-roundup-analyzing-the-holiday-season-winners-and-losers", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 16:30:00"}]}